      <arrangement id="aspace_232d8ba181312d34c950902ac6a575fa">
         <head>Arrangement</head>
         <p>Organized into five series: I. Photographs of Arizona, 2012. II. Photographs of Idaho, 2007-2013. III. Photographs of Nevada, 2012. IV. Photographs of Utah, 2010-2011. V. Photographs of Wyoming, 2013.</p>  
      </arrangement>
