      <bioghist id="aspace_1bffb2f46164f9763f9e5618821d8c27">
         <head>Laura McPhee (born 1958)</head>
         <p>Laura McPhee is a photographer. Born in New York City and raised in central New Jersey, she earned a Bachelor of Arts in Art History from Princeton University in 1980, and a Master of Fine Arts in Photography from the Rhode Island School of Design in 1986. Her work, which ranges from portrait to landscape to still life, is widely exhibited nationally and internationally. She has been a member of the faculty at the Massachusetts College of Art and Design since 1986 and lives in Brookline, Massachusetts.</p>  
      </bioghist>
